  "title": "Senior Engineer",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Strong knowledge of Nutanix architecture and components. </li>\n  <li>Proficiency in virtualization technologies such as VMware or Hyper-V. </li>\n  <li>Experience with scripting languages such as Bash, Python, or PowerShell. </li>\n  <li>Familiarity with networking concepts and technologies. </li>\n  <li>Certification in Nutanix or related fields.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Experience in backup engineering with strong exposure to enterprise environments.<br>\n• Expert in Veeam Backup &amp; Replication, including features like SureBackup, Cloud Connect, and Instant Recovery.<br>\n• Experience with AWS Backup, Azure Backup, and cloud-native workloads (e.g., EC2, Azure VMs, RDS, Azure Files).</p>\n<p>• Strong understanding of enterprise storage systems and integration with backup platforms.<br>\n• Skilled in scripting and automation (PowerShell, Bash, or Python).<br>\n• Experience with virtualization technologies (VMware, Hyper-V) in backup contexts.</p>\n<p><br></p>",
